IF IT'S ALL RIGHT,
AOI-CHAN.

249
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,625
- I'M SO GLAD.

250
00:13:19,708 --> 00:13:22,000
- I'LL DEFINITELY MAKE SURE

251
00:13:22,083 --> 00:13:23,833
THAT I GET HOME
IN TIME FOR DINNER, OKAY?

252
00:13:23,916 --> 00:13:25,791
- TAKE CARE ON YOUR WAY.

253
00:13:25,875 --> 00:13:27,291
- YEAH.

254
00:13:27,375 --> 00:13:29,666
I'M OFF THEN.

255
00:13:31,666 --> 00:13:33,125
- YES.

256
00:13:33,208 --> 00:13:34,708
I'LL DO MY BEST.

257
00:13:39,833 --> 00:13:41,458
- I'M OFF.
( chuckles )

258
00:13:41,541 --> 00:13:44,458
