I SAID THAT?

259
00:13:59,875 --> 00:14:02,125
- NOW, WELL, LET'S SEE.

260
00:14:02,208 --> 00:14:03,333
- WELCOME.
- HUH?

261
00:14:03,416 --> 00:14:05,208
- WHAT'LL IT BE, MISSUS?

262
00:14:05,291 --> 00:14:07,458
- OH MY.

263
00:14:07,541 --> 00:14:09,125
I'M NO MISSUS, SIR.

264
00:14:09,208 --> 00:14:13,458
HOWEVER, I WOULD LIKE
THE MACKEREL, PLEASE.

265
00:14:13,541 --> 00:14:15,666
- YOU BET.
THAT'S COMING RIGHT UP.

266
00:14:17,250 --> 00:14:19,125
- ( sighs )
THAT SHOULD BE ALL OF IT.

267
00:14:19,208 --> 00:14:22,125
BUT BEFORE I BEGIN
PREPARING DINNER, 

268
00:14:22,208 --> 00:14:24,833
FIRST THINGS FIRST.

269
00:14:25,916 --> 00:14:27,583
ALL RIGHT.

270
00:14:36,166 --> 00:14:37,458
( sighs )

271
00:14:37,541 --> 00:14:39,458
OH, GOODNESS,
THAT KAORU-SAMA.

272
00:14:39,541 --> 00:14:42,125
HE CERTAINLY HAD 
A LOT OF LAUNDRY.

273
00:14:42,208 --> 00:14:43,958
( sighs )
HUH?

274
00:14:46,083 --> 00:14:47,500
WHAT?

275
00:14:47,583 --> 00:14:49,750
OHH...

276
00:14:49,833 --> 00:14:53,750
- SO YOU SEE, THE RELATIONSHIP
BETWEEN A MAN AND A WOMAN CAN...

277
00:14:53,833 --> 00:14:57,041
- I WONDER WHAT KIND OF DINNER
AOI-CHAN WILL BE MAKING FOR ME.

278
00:14:57,125 --> 00:14:59,083
- ( humming )

279
00:15:14,541 --> 00:15:16,000
( sighs )

280
00:15:17,541 --> 00:15:19,125
THIS ISN'T...

281
00:15:19,208 --> 00:15:20,458
A DREAM.

282
00:15:20,541 --> 00:15:22,291
- HEY, HANABISHI.

283
00:15:22,375 --> 00:15:23,875
WE'RE GOING OUT
DRINKING TONIGHT,

284
00:15:23,958 --> 00:15:26,458
SO DON'T BE LATE.
- DRINKING TONIGHT?

285
00:15:26,541 --> 00:15:27,958
- WE TOLD YOU 
THE OTHER DAY.

286
00:15:28,041 --> 00:15:29,166
- YOU DID, HUH.

287
00:15:29,250 --> 00:15:30,833
- YOU ARE COMING,
AREN'T YOU?

288
00:15:30,916 --> 00:15:33,333
- UH, ACTUALLY...

289
00:15:33,416 --> 00:15:36,125
I'M SORRY, BUT I GOT A SUDDEN
CHANGE IN PLANS TODAY.

290
00:15:36,208 --> 00:15:38,125
- YOU SERIOUS?
HANABISHI,

291
00:15:38,208 --> 00:15:40,083
I TOLD YOU EVERY MEMBER
OF THE PHOTO CLUB

292
00:15:40,166 --> 00:15:41,375
HAD TO ATTEND.
- SORRY.

293
00:15:41,458 --> 00:15:43,791
I'LL MAKE SURE
TO GO NEXT TIME.

294
00:15:43,875 --> 00:15:45,416
- ( clock ticking )

295
00:15:51,208 --> 00:15:53,625
- I WONDER WHY IT IS
THAT WHEN I'M WITH KAORU-SAMA

296
00:15:53,708 --> 00:15:56,875
TIME SEEMS TO SLIP BY
SO QUICKLY.

297
00:16:00,208 --> 00:16:02,833
IT IS A BIT EARLY,
BUT...

298
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:10,375
KAORU-SAMA!
- HUH?

299
00:16:10,458 --> 00:16:11,625
AOI-CHAN!

300
00:16:11,708 --> 00:16:14,375
- PLEASE ALLOW ME
TO WELCOME YOU HOME.

301
00:16:14,458 --> 00:16:15,791
- I'M BACK.

302
00:16:15,875 --> 00:16:18,125
BUT WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE, AOI-CHAN?

303
00:16:18,208 --> 00:16:20,791
- I FINISHED PREPARING DINNER
SOME TIME AGO,

304
00:16:20,875 --> 00:16:22,083
SO I THOUGHT I'D WAIT.

305
00:16:22,166 --> 00:16:24,291
- YEAH, BUT I DON'T THINK
I EVER MENTIONED

306
00:16:24,375 --> 00:16:26,125
WHAT TIME I'D BE
GETTING BACK.

307
00:16:26,208 --> 00:16:28,458
WERE YOU WAITING
THE WHOLE TIME? 

308
00:16:28,541 --> 00:16:30,125
- OH, NO.

309
00:16:30,208 --> 00:16:31,791
- HOW LONG WERE YOU WAITING?

310
00:16:31,875 --> 00:16:34,458
- LET'S SEE,
AN HOUR I SUPPOSE?

311
00:16:34,541 --> 00:16:35,791
- FOR AN HOUR?

312
00:16:35,875 --> 00:16:37,625
YOU SHOULD HAVE BEEN
WAITING AT HOME.

313
00:16:37,708 --> 00:16:39,791
- FORGIVE ME.
IT'S JUST...

314
00:16:39,875 --> 00:16:42,958
I WANTED TO BE WITH YOU AGAIN
AS SOON AS POSSIBLE.

315
00:16:43,041 --> 00:16:44,375
- ( gasps )

316
00:16:44,458 --> 00:16:47,083
- ANYWAY, I WAS LOOKING
FORWARD TO SEEING YOU, 

317
00:16:47,166 --> 00:16:49,125
SO IT SEEMED LIKE
A BRIEF MOMENT TO ME.

318
00:16:49,208 --> 00:16:51,875
- OH, I SEE.

319
00:17:04,083 --> 00:17:07,416
- UM... KAORU-SAMA?

320
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:08,666
- HUH?

321
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:11,458
- I HAVE A FAVOR
TO ASK OF YOU.

322
00:17:11,541 --> 00:17:12,875
- A FAVOR?

323
00:17:12,958 --> 00:17:14,791
- WELL...

324
00:17:14,875 --> 00:17:17,291
WOULD IT BE ALL RIGHT
IF WE HELD HANDS?

325
00:17:17,375 --> 00:17:19,916
- UH... SURE.

326
00:17:22,791 --> 00:17:26,333
- I NEVER REALIZED THAT
YOUR HAND WAS SO MUCH

327
00:17:26,416 --> 00:17:27,541
BIGGER THAN MINE.

328
00:17:27,625 --> 00:17:29,291
- YOU THINK SO?
HUH.

329
00:17:29,375 --> 00:17:31,291
- YES.  HOWEVER,

330
00:17:31,375 --> 00:17:33,833
THE HAND THAT
I REMEMBER HOLDING

331
00:17:33,916 --> 00:17:35,166
WAS THAT OF A CHILD.

332
00:17:35,250 --> 00:17:39,375
IT'S ONLY NATURAL
THAT IT HAS CHANGED.

333
00:17:39,458 --> 00:17:41,000
- IF WE'RE TALKING
ABOUT CHANGES,

334
00:17:41,083 --> 00:17:43,166
THEN YOU'VE CHANGED
A LOT TOO, AOI-CHAN.

335
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:45,791
- YOU THINK THAT
I'VE CHANGED A LOT?

336
00:17:45,875 --> 00:17:47,791
- YEAH.  A LOT.

337
00:17:47,875 --> 00:17:49,208
- HOW HAVE I CHANGED?

338
00:17:49,291 --> 00:17:51,625
- YOU'VE BECOME
VERY BEAUTIFUL.

339
00:17:51,708 --> 00:17:52,625
- OH.

340
00:17:54,208 --> 00:17:56,458
OH, STOP.
YOU'RE EMBARRASSING ME.

341
00:17:56,541 --> 00:17:58,458
- ( chuckles )

342
00:18:01,208 --> 00:18:03,375
- Aoi: PLEASE,
GO AHEAD AND START.

343
00:18:03,458 --> 00:18:05,125
- WOW!

344
00:18:05,208 --> 00:18:07,083
LOOKS DELICIOUS.

345
00:18:07,166 --> 00:18:09,458
THANKS FOR ALL THE FOOD.

346
00:18:09,541 --> 00:18:11,125
( chuckles )

347
00:18:11,208 --> 00:18:13,041
WHAT'S THIS, AOI-CHAN?

348
00:18:13,125 --> 00:18:16,333
- OH. CHIKUZEN STEW.

349
00:18:16,416 --> 00:18:18,166
- ( chews ) 
- HOW IS IT?

350
00:18:18,250 --> 00:18:20,458
- MM-HMM.
- I HOPE IT IS TO YOUR LIKING.

351
00:18:20,541 --> 00:18:23,458
- IT'S GREAT.
TOTALLY DELICIOUS.

352
00:18:23,541 --> 00:18:25,125
- I'M SO GLAD.

353
00:18:25,208 --> 00:18:27,291
PLEASE EAT AS MUCH
AS YOU WOULD LIKE.

354
00:18:27,375 --> 00:18:28,958
THERE'S ENOUGH FOOD
FOR SECONDS.

355
00:18:29,041 --> 00:18:33,291
- MMM!  IT'S THE FIRST TIME
SINCE I LEFT THE HANABISHI HOUSE

356
00:18:33,375 --> 00:18:34,791
THAT I'VE EATEN
FOOD THIS GOOD.

357
00:18:34,875 --> 00:18:37,125
- IS THAT REALLY TRUE?
- MM-HMM.

358
00:18:37,208 --> 00:18:39,791
I EAT INSTANT NOODLES
MOST OF THE TIME.

359
00:18:39,875 --> 00:18:41,458
AND WHEN I DON'T
HAVE ENOUGH MONEY,

360
00:18:41,541 --> 00:18:43,458
I END UP LIVING OFF OF
BREAD CRUSTS.

361
00:18:43,541 --> 00:18:45,791
- LIVE OFF OF BREAD CRUST?

362
00:18:45,875 --> 00:18:47,958
YOU CAN'T MEAN
THAT IS ALL YOU EAT.

363
00:18:48,041 --> 00:18:49,458
- YEP.

364
00:18:49,541 --> 00:18:51,958
BUT THAT'S HOW GUYS
LIVING ALONE USUALLY EAT.

365
00:18:52,041 --> 00:18:53,791
- THAT WON'T DO!
IT WON'T.

366
00:18:53,875 --> 00:18:56,166
YOU MUST EAT SOMETHING
THAT IS MORE NUTRITIOUS.

367
00:18:56,250 --> 00:18:57,666
YOU WILL DIE OTHERWISE.

368
00:18:57,750 --> 00:19:00,166
- ( gulps )
YOU'RE OVERREACTING.

369
00:19:00,250 --> 00:19:03,125
- HERE.  I INSIST 
THAT YOU EAT THIS.

370
00:19:03,208 --> 00:19:05,750
I KNOW THAT GRILLED FISH
IS YOUR FAVORITE TOO,

371
00:19:05,833 --> 00:19:07,291
SO HAVE SOME THIS INSTANT.

372
00:19:07,375 --> 00:19:08,833
- THANKS.

373
00:19:10,541 --> 00:19:12,791
GRILLED FISH
IS MY FAVORITE.

374
00:19:12,875 --> 00:19:16,458
HOW DID AOI-CHAN KNOW
WHAT MY FAVORITE FOOD WAS?

375
00:19:16,541 --> 00:19:18,458
COME TO THINK OF IT,

376
00:19:18,541 --> 00:19:19,958
NOW THAT I LOOK AT THIS TABLE,

377
00:19:20,041 --> 00:19:21,458
THIS IS ALL FOOD
THAT I LIKE.

378
00:19:21,541 --> 00:19:24,333
- IS SOMETHING THE MATTER?

379
00:19:24,416 --> 00:19:25,791
- UH, AOI-CHAN?

380
00:19:25,875 --> 00:19:28,791
HOW DID YOU KNOW
WHAT FOOD I LIKED?

381
00:19:28,875 --> 00:19:30,750
- WELL, TO TELL THE TRUTH,

382
00:19:30,833 --> 00:19:33,000
I WAS CONSTANTLY WATCHING YOU
WHEN WE WERE STILL CHILDREN,

383
00:19:33,083 --> 00:19:34,750
KAORU-SAMA.

384
00:19:34,833 --> 00:19:38,500
I ALSO LEARNED MANY OTHER THINGS
ABOUT YOU DURING THAT TIME.

385
00:19:38,583 --> 00:19:40,500
THAT YOU LIKED GRILLED FISH,

386
00:19:40,583 --> 00:19:43,125
THAT YOUR FAVORITE COLOR
IS BLUE,

387
00:19:43,208 --> 00:19:45,208
THAT YOU PREFER SHORT HAIR,

388
00:19:45,291 --> 00:19:47,416
AND WHAT KIND OF SONGS
YOU LIKE TOO.

389
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:49,791
- SONGS?

390
00:19:49,875 --> 00:19:50,791
( gasps )

391
00:19:50,875 --> 00:19:52,458
THAT'S RIGHT.

392
00:19:52,541 --> 00:19:54,791
I WAS WONDERING WHY
AOI-CHAN KNEW THAT SONG

393
00:19:54,875 --> 00:19:56,458
THAT MOTHER ALWAYS SANG.

394
00:19:56,541 --> 00:19:59,000
BUT NOW I REMEMBER.

395
00:20:00,541 --> 00:20:01,791
IT WAS ME.

396
00:20:01,875 --> 00:20:05,500
I TAUGHT HER
THAT SONG BACK THEN.

397
00:20:05,583 --> 00:20:08,291
I'M SURPRISED
YOU REMEMBER THAT SONG.

398
00:20:08,375 --> 00:20:10,458
- THERE'S NO WAY THAT
I WOULD FORGET THE SONG

399
00:20:10,541 --> 00:20:12,791
THAT YOU TAUGHT ME
WHEN WE WERE KIDS.

400
00:20:12,875 --> 00:20:15,333
I SING IT ON OCCASION
TO THIS DAY.

401
00:20:15,416 --> 00:20:18,833
I FELT CLOSER TO YOU
WHENEVER I SANG THAT SONG.

402
00:20:18,916 --> 00:20:21,708
AS IF I COULD OVERCOME
ANY PAINFUL TIMES.

403
00:20:21,791 --> 00:20:22,750
- PAINFUL TIMES?

404
00:20:22,833 --> 00:20:25,375
- YOU KNOW,
I HAVE DONE MY UPMOST

405
00:20:25,458 --> 00:20:27,625
SO THAT I COULD BE 
A GOOD WIFE TO YOU.

406
00:20:27,708 --> 00:20:30,791
IT WAS MY ONE DREAM TO BE
TOGETHER WITH YOU LIKE THIS.

407
00:20:32,208 --> 00:20:34,791
I WANT TO CLEAN UP
AFTER YOU.

408
00:20:34,875 --> 00:20:39,125
I WANT TO DO
THE LAUNDRY FOR YOU.

409
00:20:39,208 --> 00:20:40,791
I WANT TO PREPARE
MEALS FOR YOU

410
00:20:40,875 --> 00:20:43,333
THAT YOU WILL ENJOY.

411
00:20:44,875 --> 00:20:46,458
AS LONG AS YOU WISH IT,

412
00:20:46,541 --> 00:20:48,583
I WOULD LIKE TO
FULFILL THAT DESIRE.

413
00:20:48,666 --> 00:20:50,625
- AOI-CHAN...

414
00:20:50,708 --> 00:20:51,791
- FORGIVE ME.

415
00:20:51,875 --> 00:20:54,125
I DID NOT MEAN
TO CHATTER AWAY.

416
00:20:54,208 --> 00:20:56,458
PLEASE FINISH THIS
BEFORE IT GETS COLD.

417
00:20:56,541 --> 00:20:57,833
- SURE.

418
00:20:57,916 --> 00:20:59,708
- ( water sloshing )

419
00:21:01,208 --> 00:21:02,500
- ( sighs )

420
00:21:02,583 --> 00:21:03,916
I NEVER KNEW.

421
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:06,666
TO THINK THAT AOI-CHAN
HAD FELT THAT DEEPLY ABOUT ME

422
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:09,416
FOR ALL THESE YEARS.

423
00:21:09,500 --> 00:21:11,458
AND SHE'S SO THOUGHTFUL.

424
00:21:11,541 --> 00:21:14,458
SHE EVEN HAD A BATH ALREADY
DRAWN FOR ME AFTER DINNER.

425
00:21:14,541 --> 00:21:16,791
SHE REALLY IS DOING
EVERYTHING FOR ME. 

426
00:21:16,875 --> 00:21:18,791
WHICH MEANS, NEXT IS...

427
00:21:19,875 --> 00:21:21,458
- KAORU-SAMA...

428
00:21:21,541 --> 00:21:23,125
ALLOW ME TO
SCRUB YOUR BACK.

429
00:21:24,833 --> 00:21:26,458
- IF SHE DID
COME IN LIKE THAT,

430
00:21:26,541 --> 00:21:28,791
I REALLY WOULD
FALL FOR HER. 

431
00:21:28,875 --> 00:21:30,125
BUT, YOU KNOW,

432
00:21:30,208 --> 00:21:32,458
I REALLY CAN'T SEE
AOI-CHAN DOING THAT.

433
00:21:32,541 --> 00:21:33,750
- ( knocks on door )
- ( gasps )

434
00:21:33,833 --> 00:21:36,333
- KAORU-SAMA, EXCUSE ME?

435
00:21:36,416 --> 00:21:38,291
- ( gasps )

436
00:21:38,375 --> 00:21:41,458
- I WOULD LIKE TO
SCRUB YOUR BACK. 

437
00:21:41,541 --> 00:21:44,833
SO WOULD YOU MIND TERRIBLY
IF I CAME IN?

438
00:21:46,375 --> 00:21:48,125
- WHAT?!

439
00:21:48,208 --> 00:21:51,208
- ( dogs howling )

440
00:21:51,291 --> 00:21:53,166
- ( theme music playing )

441
00:21:55,541 --> 00:21:57,416
- ( singing in Japanese )

442
00:23:21,208 --> 00:23:24,916
- YOU BEAST! HOW DARE YOU
DO THIS TO LADY AOI!

443
00:23:25,000 --> 00:23:27,166
- Aoi: MISS MIYABI!

444
00:23:27,250 --> 00:23:29,791
NEXT EPISODE AI YORI AOSHI,

445
00:23:29,875 --> 00:23:32,208
"SEPARATION."

446
00:23:32,291 --> 00:23:35,166
I WILL ALWAYS BE
BY YOUR SIDE.

